room_title: Escape room "Commie Trickery" by 307 Mysteries in Gillette
room_description: You and your friends are scientists that have discovered the cure to cancer. You were about to announce it to the world, but the Russians stole the paperwork with your discovery on it. You have one hour to find your paperwork and the key to get out of the office before the Russians show up and we never hear from you again...
